rating_comment:
Good place for what there is in Siliguri.
We liked the place and Pranoy gave us everything we asked for and needed. Recommendable.
Value for money stay with clean room and nice sorrounding. Easy access to market and all with some very nice cafes in around the house.

Rude behaviour
No amenities
Dirty room and furniture
Non functional kitchen
Defunct fridge
No room service
Pranoy's place is great - very well located, clean and communication was easy and quick.

Very nice stay, Pranab is very positive and kind. The place is confortable and quite clean. One can't really cook out of the microwave owen but the neighbourhood is full of good and cheap restaurants Beginning with Pranab's one downstairs.
A cozy place to crash and have a nice vacation for a family of 2 or 3. The host is very helpful and attends to all your queries.

Great host. Pranoy and his family went out of the way to provide us with all the help they could muster and I am saying this cuz we needed a lot of it cuz of the wedding in the family. Small place but really BIG heart. And as the saying goes, heart is all that matters...

I stayed only 1 night and it was nice experience, easy to find the location, if you are coming from Darjeeling and Sikkim and can't find their location you can contact with host once you reach at (SNT Bus stand) he will help you to reach home safely. Thank you for your best hospitality keep it up hope to see you in near future.
Average and good for only two people

Decent value for money with an awesome host and a great cafe downstairs.
Basic amenities can be a bit better.
okay

Nice place to stay.
The location is good and the behavior I received from the host and his family was also pleasant. I would recommend others to stay in his place if you are in siliguri:)
Great experience, humble treatment, easily accessible house owner. Calm and quiet surroundings, yet easy to reach out for Train, Airport or main junction (Town)

A nice apartment in a quiet street in an otherwise noisy and bustly Siliguri. Close to amenities like cab ranks and street food stalls. Pranoy and his staff are available to assist in sorting out any questions or issues. Pranoy is proactive in suggestions and can assist in organising car rental etc.
This was second time we stayed with Pranoy. All is great and as it should be. Would recommend.

The host Pranoy shared the care taker's number and asked us to communicate with him.
We're disappointed with the care taker. He didn't bother to explain anything at first. We thought there were no toiletries so we had to go out to get them. There was no communication from his end about the breakfast. He saw us going out for breakfast still said nothing. It's difficult to find any breakfast place open at 7:00 in Siliguri we were flying the same day and had to be at the airport by 9:30 AM.
Clean and stylish apartment. Friendly hosts. Good location and fast internet.
The location was accurate and place had so many plants and trees. The room itself was tidy and neatly maintained. Every amenity was present. Would love to come back again
What kind people! I have so enjoyed staying here. The apartment is spacious and clean, and there are amazingly efficient ceiling fans that keep the apartment very temperate.

We stayed just for a night..still it was really satisfying as the facility was well maintained ,very clean and had homely feeling...had all the arrangements like food and drop to njp station done by the host..he was very helpful and polite.. food arranged was great..location wise also good..i would highly recommend this property

Great place to stay, easygoing and a friendly neighborhood and an awsome host.
Pranoy's place has got it all, a good and ckean environment inside and surroundings, the location is on google maps and extremely easy to find whether you arrive to the city by Bus, Train or Flight.
A good caring host and a caretaker Nasser available on the phone if you need something.

Amazing place, great hosts. Location wise also the place is not far from most of the attractions. Place is neat and clean, spacious, comfortable. Food is available on order. If you want to spend quality time away from the chaos and noise of city, this is the place. Same as shown in pictures. Go ahead and avail the great hospitality they offer. You won't regret staying there.
Nice Place for a short trip
A very nice homestay. Pranoy was super helpful. There's lots of space and the apartment was very clean, I recommend.
